The '''Consulate General of the Federal Republic of Germany in Chennai''' represents the interests of the [[Germany|German government]] in the [[Chennai]] and surrounding regions. The current Consul General is Stefan Weckbach since August 2011. He succeeds Hans-Burkhardt Sauerteig.

==Location==
The Consulate General is located at 9, Boat Club Road, [[R.A.Puram|Raja Annamalai Puram]]. Until 2006, it was located at 22, Ethiraj Road, Egmore.<ref>{{cite news
